title: It lets you see the change history.
pid: 1b11a7b9-1e6b-4d6f-b0d8-9c09e73ed0de
body: |2-
  Can be important for finding when something broke,
  to determine what broke it.
  Or to determine when a line of code was written,
  to see what was going on at that time,
  to understand what its author (probably you!) was thinking.

  AIs are great at navigating this data,
  but only if you've been collecting it.
